# {{PROJECT_NAME}} onboarding checklist

Use this file to roll the workflow out without turning it into ritual.

## Day 0
- confirm the selected profile in `README.md`
- verify backend and test globs are correct
- replace generic instructions with repository-specific constraints
- record real build, lint, test, and smoke commands

## First task
- choose one bounded backend change
- use the generated prompts instead of free-form chat first
- keep the task small enough to review fully
- note where the workflow felt heavy, vague, or redundant

## End of first week
- remove files the team did not use
- tighten prompts or instructions that were too generic
- decide whether to escalate or de-escalate the profile
- only add optional bundles if a real gap remains
